Classes to use for lepton2:

    Frame - wrapper for in-flight frame
    VulkanContext - wrapper for logicaldevice and other top-level functionality
    DeletableResourceTracker - recursive structure to track deletable resources
    Framebuffer - framebuffer
    VulkanImage - image with assoc. memory chonklet and view
    VulkanBuffer - buffer with assoc. memory chonklet
    MemoryChonkus - wrapper for single vk memory allocation (plural: chonki)
    MemoryChonklet - Subregion of a chonkus
    AllocationManager - builds, destroys, and copies chonki as needed to do allocations
    Shader - shader module
    SwapChain - wrapper for swap chain
    Subpass - manually specified, or a few subpass archetypes {
        Subpass3D - generic 3-D rendering thing
        SubpassBlindfold (has blindfold geometry and vert shader built in)
    }
    SubpassDependency
    RenderPassInformation - generates a renderpass
    RenderPipeline
    MainLoopContainer